#: templates/ktexteditor6-plugin/ktexteditor6-plugin.kdevtemplate:3
msgctxt "Name"
msgid "C++ Plugin (KF6)"
msgstr "ສ່ວນເສີມ C++ (KF6)"

#: templates/ktexteditor6-plugin/ktexteditor6-plugin.kdevtemplate:38
msgctxt "Comment"
msgid ""
"Generates a KTextEditor C++ plugin to perform special operations on text in "
"KWrite, Kate, KDevelop etc."
msgstr ""
"ສ້າງສ່ວນເສີມ C++ ຂອງ KTextEditor ເພື່ອປະຕິບັດການພິເສດກັບຂໍ້ຄວາມໃນ KWrite, "
"Kate, KDevelop ແລະ ອື່ນໆ."
